### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get one contact by id
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/PON_UN_ID_REAL_AQUI

### Create new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Luis",
  "lastName": "Perez",
  "email": "luis@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Azul",
  "birthday": "1995-06-10"
}

### Update contact by id
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/PON_UN_ID_REAL_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Luis",
  "lastName": "Perez Updated",
  "email": "luis@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Verde",
  "birthday": "1995-06-10"
}

### Delete contact by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/PON_UN_ID_REAL_AQUI